review: The delivery was incredibly **smooth** and arrived earlier than the estimated time. The delivery boy was very **polite and professional**, confirming the delivery details before handing over the package. A really positive experience overall with Zap Shift Delivery!

The package delivery took a **bit longer than expected** and missed the promised window by several hours. The tracking updates were a little sparse toward the end, which was frustrating. However, the item arrived safely and the condition was okay overall.

Absolutely **excellent service!** The pickup and delivery process was incredibly **fast and secure**. The communication from the team was clear, and I felt confident my parcel was in good hands throughout the entire journey. Highly recommend Zap Shift for urgent deliveries.

The support team was **very responsive** when I had a question about the delivery address change. The driver was also **professional** upon arrival and handled the package with care. A solid service experience, though a slightly faster transit time would be great.

The delivery was unfortunately **late**, and I received virtually **no updates** after the initial pickup confirmation. I had to call customer service multiple times for status checks, which was time-consuming. I am quite disappointed with this particular delivery experience.

What a **superb experience** from start to finish! The online booking was straightforward, the parcel was picked up exactly on time, and the delivery was quick and efficient. I will absolutely be using Zap Shift Delivery again. **Highly recommended!**

The delivery was **decent** in terms of speed, but I noticed the **packaging could definitely be better**. The box arrived with a small dent, though the contents were fine. A little more care with handling fragile items would certainly improve the overall customer satisfaction.

A **fast, safe, and friendly delivery service**—exactly what I look for! The driver was very courteous, and the real-time tracking feature worked perfectly, giving me an accurate delivery window. I appreciate the high standard of service provided by Zap Shift.
